      "writtenOn": "2026-07-03T11:45:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Redfish does not state the error response code explicitly.\n\nCurrently, GenerateSecretKeyRequired is treated as 403 Forbidden, which would incorrectly imply the session was not created, when it should be treated as an informational message accompanying a successful session creation (with 201 response code), exactly like `PasswordChangeRequired`.\n\nReference: https://www.dmtf.org/sites/default/files/standards/documents/DSP0266_1.24.0.pdf#page\u003d202\u0026zoom\u003d100,0,789",
      "parentUuid": "35fb497f_451716a0",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 11,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 11,
        "endChar": 40
      },
      "revId": "d61e82e6ef2c3dfedd6ee009a562b1fe906aee23",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "4550469e_985d0329",
        "filename": "/COMMIT_MSG",
        "patchSetId": 3
      },
      "lineNbr": 11,
      "author": {
        "id": 1001604
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-16T17:27:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The specification seems indicating that there are a few special cases that may be treated successful or informational, but all other cases would be forbidden.\n\nThe spec - https://www.dmtf.org/sites/default/files/standards/documents/DSP0266_1.24.0.pdf#page\u003d202\u0026zoom\u003d100,0,789 says:\n\n```\n...\u003cspecial cases\u003e ...\n\nFor all other operations, the service shall respond with the HTTP 403 Forbidden status code and an error response\nwith the GenerateSecretKeyRequired message from the Base Message Registry.\n```\n\nThen, should the message generation be separated like `GenerateSecretKeyRequiredInformational`?\n\nOr should we ask DMTF to change the spec about `403 Forbidden` as `informational`?",
      "parentUuid": "4c5ff0a1_5714a583",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 11,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 11,
        "endChar": 40
      },
      "revId": "d61e82e6ef2c3dfedd6ee009a562b1fe906aee23",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
